%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETesla%20is%20set%20to%20go%20to%20trial%20Tuesday%20over%20a%20wrongful%20death%20lawsuit%20regarding%20a%20fatal%20crash%20in%202018.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20deposition%20from%20a%20Tesla%20engineer%20obtained%20by%20WaPo%20reveals%20how%20Tesla's%20autopilot%20works.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20engineer%20testified%20under%20oath%20that%20the%20autopilot%20follows%C2%A0%26quot%3Bclearly%20marked%20lane%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20WaPo.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENewly%20reported%20testimony%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20engineer%20is%20providing%20rare%20insight%20into%20how%20the%20electric%20car's%20autopilot%20feature%20functions%20and%20what%20occurred%20at%20the%20time%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-engineer-walter-huang-family-suing-tesla-over-crash-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efatal%202018%20car%20crash%20in%20California%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20set%20to%20go%20to%20trial%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20a%20wrongful-death%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20the%20family%20of%20Walter%20Huang%2C%20an%20Apple%20engineer%20who%20died%20in%20March%202018%20after%20his%20Model%20X%20crashed%20into%20a%20safety%20barrier%20on%20a%20California%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20accuses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%20company%20of%20misleading%20consumers%20about%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-autopilot-safety-assisted-self-driving-systems-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecar's%20autopilot%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20knowingly%20rolling%20out%20a%20%26quot%3Bdefective%26quot%3B%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202023%2C%20attorneys%20for%20Huang's%20family%20deposed%20Akshay%20Phatak%2C%20a%20Tesla%20engineer%2C%20to%20get%20further%20insight%20into%20how%20the%20vehicle's%20autopilot%20system%20functions.%20The%20deposition%20was%20obtained%20and%20reported%20on%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftechnology%2F2024%2F04%2F07%2Ftesla-autopilot-crash-trial%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20engineer%20revealed%20to%20the%20family's%20lawyers%20that%20the%20car%20steers%20itself%20by%20relying%20on%20marked%20lanes%20on%20the%20highway%20%E2%80%94%20a%20design%20similar%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fntsb-calls-for-collision-prevention-tech-2012-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elane%20departure%20warning%3C%2Fa%3E%20systems%20that%20can%20be%20found%20in%20many%20modern%20cars%2C%20but%20one%20that%20Tesla%20has%20advertised%20as%20part%20of%20its%20advanced%20%26quot%3Bautopilot%26quot%3B%20technology%2C%20the%20Post%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20are%20clearly%20marked%20lane%20lines%2C%20the%20system%20will%20follow%20the%20lane%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20Phatak%20said%20under%20oath%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Post.%20He%20added%20that%20Tesla's%20system%20was%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%26quot%3B%20to%20follow%20the%20lane%20lines%20of%20the%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20attorneys%20for%20the%20Huang%20family%2C%20Huang%20was%20driving%20on%20a%20highway%20with%20autopilot%20activated%20when%20his%20Model%20X%20approached%20a%20%26quot%3Bpaved%20gore%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20buffer%20zone%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elocated%20at%20the%20intersection%20of%20a%20highway%20and%20an%20exit%20ramp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20autopilot%20feature%20then%20turned%20Huang's%20vehicle%20%26quot%3Bleft%2C%20out%20of%20the%20designated%20travel%20lane%2C%20and%20drove%20it%20straight%20into%20a%20concrete%20highway%20median%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20attorneys%20claimed%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Post%20reported%20the%20car%20drifted%20as%20the%20lane%20markings%20on%20the%20highway%20faded.%20According%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20vehicle%20then%20detected%20a%20clearer%20marking%20on%20the%20left%2C%20pulling%20the%20car%20and%20making%20it%20head%20straight%20for%20the%20barrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20during%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChief%20among%20Tesla's%20defenses%20is%20that%20the%20crash%20was%20ultimately%20due%20to%20Huang's%20inattentiveness.%20Tesla's%20attorneys%20argued%20in%20a%20court%20filing%20that%20had%20Huang%20%26quot%3Bbeen%20paying%20attention%20to%20the%20road%20he%20would%20have%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20avoid%20this%20crash%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fautos-transportation%2Fnext-autopilot-trial-test-teslas-blame-the-driver-defense-2024-03-11%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20Tesla%20plan%20to%20bring%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-apple-autopilot-crash-wrongful-death-lawsuit-playing-video-games-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etestimony%20from%20an%20Apple%20engineer%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20claims%20that%20data%20from%20Huang's%20iPhone%20indicates%20he%20was%20using%20his%20device%20before%20the%20fatal%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20previously%20concluded%20in%20its%20probe%20that%20there%20was%20no%20singular%20cause%20for%20the%20crash.%20The%20agency%20said%20that%20Tesla's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eautopilot%20had%20%26quot%3Bsystem%20limitations%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20vehicle's%20%26quot%3Bineffective%20monitoring%20of%20driver%20engagement%26quot%3B%20contributed%20to%20the%20driver's%20%26quot%3Bcomplacency%20and%20inattentiveness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhatak%20also%20said%20in%20his%20deposition%20that%20Tesla's%20autopilot%20system%20will%20work%20as%20long%20the%20car's%20cameras%20detect%20markers%20on%20the%20road%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Post%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20there%20are%20painted%20lane%20lines%2C%20the%20system%20will%20follow%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Phatak%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Post%20previously%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-autopilot-crashes-activating-unsuitable-roads-regulator2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla's%20assisted-driving%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20sometimes%20enabled%20on%20roads%20for%20which%20it's%20not%20designed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20for%20the%20Huang%20family%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20during%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-autopilot-lane-markings-2018-fatal-crash-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712543578000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66133d4616bde8d4ead66130%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-autopilot-lane-markings-2018-fatal-crash-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Tesla%20engineer%20said%20in%20a%20deposition%20for%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20EV%20company%20that%20Tesla%20relies%20on%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20marked%20lines%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20autopilot%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A128%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-autopilot-lane-markings-2018-fatal-crash-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HSBC%20helps%20overseas%20funds%20navigate%20India's%20bond%20market%20as%20inclusion%20nears%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2