quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work.%20We%20had%20to%20clear%20our%20minds%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20believed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20skipper%20as%20his%20team%20played%20the%20first%20game%20after%20six-day%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBatting%20at%20No%207%2C%20Guyanese%20all-rounder%20Romario%20Shepherd%20single-handedly%20took%20the%20match%20out%20of%20DC's%20reach%2C%20smashing%20Anrich%20Nortje%20for%2032%20runs%20in%20the%20last%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20some%20hitting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20Romario's%2039%20not%20out%20from%2010%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20won%20us%20the%20game.%20Difference%20was%20Romario%20versus%20Delhi%20Capitals.%20I%20like%20him.%20Always%20has%20a%20smile%20on%20his%20face%2C%20doesn't%20run%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMI%20have%20finally%20got%20their%20combination%20right%20and%20this%20is%20the%20way%20forward%2C%20said%20Hardik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20be%20making%20tactical%20changes%20here%20and%20there%20but%20this%20will%20be%20our%2012%20and%20settling%20our%20team%20now%20is%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik%20was%20not%20seen%20bowling%20in%20the%20past%20two%20games%20and%20the%20star%20India%20all-rounder%20said%20he%20would%20bowl%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20fine.%20I'll%20be%20bowling%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%20we%20had%20everything%20covered%20today%20so%20did%20not%20have%20to%20roll%20my%20arms%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShepherd%20approached%20with%20a%20clear%20mind%20and%20said%20his%20hard%20work%20at%20the%20nets%20has%20%26quot%3Bpaid%20off%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20hard%20work%20has%20paid%20off.%20I%20have%20put%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work%20in%20the%20nets.%20I%20think%20you%20just%20have%20to%20keep%20a%20clear%20mind%20(when%20batting%20at%20the%20end).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Tim%20David)%20said%20no%20you%20stay%20there%20(strike)%20and%20you%20hit.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20good%20position%20to%20capitalise%20on%20that%20ball.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeed%20to%20improve%20death%20over%20bowling%3A%20Pant%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Delhi%20Capitals%2C%20this%20was%20their%20fourth%20loss%20from%20five%20matches%20as%20they%20languish%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20standings%20and%20skipper%20Rishabh%20Pant%20blamed%20it%20on%20their%20poor%20batting%20and%20death%20overs%20bowling.%20Anrich%20Nortje%20gave%20away%2032%20runs%20in%20the%20final%20over%20which%20cost%20DC%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bowlers%20needed%20to%20bowl%20into%20the%20wicket%2C%20slower%20ones%20and%20the%20variations%20were%20important.%20The%20bowlers%20needed%20to%20understand%20the%20conditions%20well.%20I%20think%20we%20need%20to%20improve%20on%20a%20few%20areas%20--%20death-over%20bowling%20and%20our%20batting%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%20Delhi%20Capitals%20imposing%20chase%20of%20235%20was%20ignited%20by%20Tristan%20Stubbs%2071%20not%20out%20from%2025%20balls.%20But%20he%20lacked%20support%20at%20the%20other%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefinitely%2C%20we%20were%20in%20contention%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20have%20enough%20runs%20in%20the%20batting%20powerplay%2C%20especially%20when%20you're%20chasing%20such%20a%20big%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20batted%20well%20in%20the%20next%20few%20overs%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20easy%20to%20constantly%20score%2015%20runs%20per%20over%20for%20many%20overs.%20Yes%2C%20we%20had%20a%20few%20bad%20overs%20(with%20the%20ball)%2C%20but%20it%20does%20happen%20at%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Pant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712543340000%2C%22v