2https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdiljit-dosanjh-confesses-acting-is-not-his-forte%2Farticleshow%2F109117418.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Total%20Solar%20Eclipse%20Today%3A%20Why%20India's%20Sun%20Satellite%20Won't%20Catch%20A%20Glimpse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20first%20space-based%20solar%20observatory%2C%20Aditya%20L1%2C%20is%20continuously%20studying%20the%20Sun%20but%20will%20miss%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Ftotal-solar-eclipse-on-april-8-time-duration-and-how-to-watch-it-live-online-5392106%5C%22%3Etotal%20solar%20eclipse%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%20that%20will%20be%20visible%20over%20vast%20swaths%20of%20North%20America.%20The%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20is%20a%20rare%20event%20that%20people%20across%20the%20USA%20and%20several%20events%2C%20from%20skydiving%20to%20special%20flights%2C%20are%20being%20organized%20to%20witness%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Ftotal-solar-eclipse-2024-will-this-rare-celestial-event-be-visible-in-india-5392904%5C%22%3Ecelestial%20phenomenon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20almost%20a%20century%2C%20the%20western%20and%20northern%20parts%20of%20New%20York%20State%20will%20experience%20a%20total%20eclipse.%20The%20path%20of%20totality%20-%20a%20narrow%20stretch%20where%20the%20Moon%20obscures%20the%20Sun%20entirely%20-%20tracks%20across%20cities%20and%20has%20set%20the%20USA%20into%20a%20tizzy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20statement%20about%20the%20event%2C%20NASA%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20April%208%2C%202024%2C%20a%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20will%20cross%20North%20America%2C%20passing%20over%20Mexico%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20Canada.%20A%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20happens%20when%20the%20Moon%20passes%20between%20the%20Sun%20and%20Earth%2C%20completely%20blocking%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Sun.%20The%20sky%20will%20darken%20as%20if%20it%20were%20dawn%20or%20dusk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20is%20also%20flying%20special%20research%20planes%20to%20chase%20the%20shadow%20among%20many%20other%20experiments.%20Though%20the%20entire%20event%20will%20last%20for%20several%20hours%2C%20the%20main%20spectacle%20-%20when%20day%20turns%20to%20night%20-%20is%20expected%20to%20last%20only%20about%20four%20minutes%20when%20there%20will%20be%20total%20darkness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faditya-l1-enters-final-orbit-pm-says-india-creates-yet-another-landmark-4811259%5C%22%3EIndia's%20Aditya%20L1%20satellite%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20witness%20the%20event.%20This%20is%20not%20because%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organization%20(ISRO)%20has%20erred%2C%20but%20because%20the%20satellite%20is%20placed%20appropriately%20at%20a%20location%20that%20provides%20an%20uninterrupted%2024x7%2C%20365-day%20view%20of%20the%20Sun.%20The%20Indian%20scientists%20chose%20a%20spot%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20satellite's%20view%20is%20never%20blocked%20due%20to%20an%20eclipse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAditya%20L1%20spacecraft%20will%20not%20see%20the%20solar%20eclipse%20as%20the%20moon%20is%20behind%20the%20spacecraft%2C%20at%20the%20Lagrange%20Point%201%20(L1%20point)%2C%20the%20eclipse%20that%20is%20visible%20on%20Earth%20doesn't%20have%20much%20significance%20at%20that%20location%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20chairman%20S.%20Somanath%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Aditya%20L1%20spacecraft%20is%20placed%20in%20a%20halo%20orbit%20around%20the%20Lagrange%20point%201%20(L1)%20of%20the%20Sun-Earth%20system%2C%20which%20is%20about%201.5%20million%20km%20from%20Earth.%20A%20satellite%20placed%20in%20the%20halo%20orbit%20around%20the%20L1%20point%20has%20the%20major%20advantage%20of%20continuously%20viewing%20the%20Sun%20without%20any%20occultation%20or%20eclipses.%20This%20provides%20a%20greater%20advantage%20of%20observing%20solar%20activity%20and%20its%20effect%20on%20space%20weather%20in%20real-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F7unhk298_l1-sun-point_625x300_08_April_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%20L1%20weighs%20nearly%201%2C500%20kilograms%20and%20is%20a%20scientific%20robotic%20satellite%20to%20keep%20a%20continuous%20eye%20on%20the%20Sun.%20This%20is%20India's%20first%20dedicated%20mission%20to%20monitor%20the%20Sun%2C%20especially%20to%20understand%20what%20happens%20when%20the%20Sun%20becomes%20active.%20The%20solar%20observatory%20has%20been%20made%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%20400%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Aditya%20L1%20satellite%20creates%20its%20own%20artificial%20solar%20eclipse%20to%20effectively%20study%20the%20Sun%20with%20its%20special%20instrument%2C%20the%20Visible%20Emission%20Line%20Coronagraph%20(VELC).%20Mr.%20Somanath%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20solar%20eclipse%20is%20created%20in%20the%20coronagraph%20by%20eliminating%20the%20light%20from%20the%20disc%20of%20the%20Sun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Dipankar%20Banerjee%2C%20a%20solar%20physicist%20with%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20(IIAP)%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20says%20the%20spacecraft%20offers%20scientists%20the%20opportunity%20to%20see%20and%20study%20the%20corona%20of%20the%20Sun%20as%20seen%20from%20space%20and%20as%20viewed%20from%20the%20ground%20during%20a%20total%20solar%20eclipse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Banerjee%20will%20be%20conducting%20some%20experiments%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Dallas%2C%20Texas%2C%20USA%2C%20during%20today's%20eclipse%2C%20and%20that%20data%20will%20be%20compared%20with%20Aditya%20L1%20data%20for%20the%20same%20viewing%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENigar%20Shaji%2C%20the%20Project%20Director%20for%20the%20Aditya%20L1%20satellite%20from%20ISRO%2C%20says%20that%20nothing%20will%20change%20in%20the%20Sun%20due%20to%20the%20eclipse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20the%20eclipse%2C%20nothing%20special%20happens%20to%20the%20Sun.%20The%20VELC%20spectroscopic%20channels%20will%20be%20operated%20in%20raster%20scan%20and%20sit%20and%20stare%20mode%20of%20operation%20%5Bspecial%20observation%20modes%5D%20to%20observe%20the%20coronal%20structures%20in%20emission%20lines.%20This%20will%20be%20a%20joint%20campaign%20to%20corroborate%20with%20ground-based%20observations%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms.%20Shaji%20tells%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%20L1%20carries%20seven%20payloads%20to%20observe%20the%20photosphere%2C%20chromosphere%2C%20and%20the%20outermost%20layers%20of%20the%20Sun%20(the%20corona)%20using%20electromagnetic%2C%20particle%2C%20and%20magnetic%20field%20detectors.%20Using%20the%20special%20vantage%20point%20L1%2C%20four%20payloads%20directly%20view%20the%20Sun%2C%20and%20the%20remaining%20three%20payloads%20carry%20out%20in-situ%20studies%20of%20particles%20and%20fields%20at%20the%20Lagrange%20point%20L1%2C%20thus%20providing%20important%20scientific%20studies%20of%20the%20effect%20of%20solar%20dynamics%20in%20the%20interplanetary%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECautionary%20Note%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BExcept%20during%20the%20brief%20total%20phase%20of%20a%20total%20solar%20eclipse%2C%20when%20the%20Moon%20completely%20blocks%20the%20Sun's%20bright%20face%2C%20it%20is%20not%20safe%20to%20look%20directly%20at%20the%20Sun%20without%20specialized%20eye%20protection%20for%20solar%20viewing.%20Viewing%20any%20part%20of%20the%20bright%20Sun%20through%20a%20camera%20lens%2C%20binoculars%2C%20or%20a%20telescope%20without%20a%20special-purpose%20solar%20filter%20secured%20over%20the%20front%20of%20the%20optics%20will%20instantly%20cause%20severe%20eye%20injury.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712542200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fnhjqb2ck_solar-eclipse-getty_625x300_08_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftotal-solar-eclipse-today-why-india-sun-satellite-aditya-l1-wont-catch-a-glimpse-5396432%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20first%20space-based%20solar%20observatory%2C%20Aditya%20L1%2C%20is%20continuously%20studying%20the%20Sun%20but%20will%20miss%20the%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20today%20that%20will%20be%20visible%20over%20vast%20swaths%20of%20North%20America.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftotal-solar-eclipse-today-why-india-sun-satellite-aditya-l1-wont-catch-a-glimpse-5396432%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftotal-solar-eclipse-today-why-india-sun-satellite-aditya-l1-wont-catch-a-glimpse-5396432%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftotal-solar-eclipse-today-why-india-sun-satellite-aditya-l1-wont-catch-a-glimpse-5396432%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sara%20drops%20pics%20from%20vacay%20with%20Ibrahim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712542050000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109117371%2Cimgsize-34424.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsara-ali-khan-drops-photos-from-her-vacay-time-with-ibrahim-ali-khan-says-shes-a-peace-loving-person-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F109117367.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109117367.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESara%20Ali%20Khan%20is%20on%20a%20holiday%20with%20her%20brother%20Ibrahim%20Ali%20Khan%20and%20netizens%20speculate%20that%20Ibrahim's%20rumoured%20girlfriend%20Palak%20Tiwari%20is%20also%20with%20them%20as%20she%20was%20also%20spotted%20at%20the%20airport%20yesterday!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsara-ali-khan-drops-photos-from-her-vacay-time-with-ibrahim-ali-khan-says-shes-a-peace-loving-person-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F109117367.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Qutub%20Minar%20Illuminates%20In%20Remembrance%20Of%20Rwanda%20Genocide%20Of%201994%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Qutub%20Minar%20was%20lit%20up%20with%20the%20colours%20of%20the%20Rwandan%20national%20flag%20on%20Sunday%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20the%20east-African%20nation%20in%20remembrance%20of%20the%20100-day%20massacre%20that%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20800%2C000%20people%20in%201994.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20occasion%2C%20Secretary%20(Economic%20Relations)%20Dammu%20Ravi%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20represented%20India%20at%20the%2030th%20commemoration%20of%20the%20genocide%20in%20the%20Rwanda%20capital%2C%20Kigali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20official%20spokesperson%20of%20MEA%2C%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%2C%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Rwanda%2C%20India%20lit%20up%20the%20Qutub%20Minar%20today%2C%20marking%20the%20UN%20International%20Day%20of%20Reflection%20on%20the%201994%20Genocide%20against%20the%20Tutsi%20in%20Rwanda.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecy%20(ER)%20Dammu%20Ravi%20represented%20India%20at%20the%2030th%20commemoration%20of%20the%20genocide%20today%20in%20Kigali%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERwanda%20marked%2030%20years%20of%20the%20genocide%20orchestrated%20by%20armed%20Hutu%20extremists%2C%20who%20tore%20apart%20the%20nation.%20The%201994%20Rwanda%20Genocide%20(Kwibuka%2030)%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20bloodiest%20massacres%20of%20the%2020th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Al%20Jazeera%2C%20Rwanda's%20President%20Paul%20Kagame%20led%20the%20commemoration%20on%20Sunday%20by%20placing%20wreaths%20on%20the%20mass%20graves%20in%20the%20country's%20capital%2C%20Kigali.%20The%20event%20was%20flanked%20by%20several%20foreign%20dignitaries%2C%20including%20the%20South%20African%20leaders%2C%20as%20well%20as%20dignitaries%20from%20Ethiopia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20US%20President%20Bill%20Clinton%20was%20also%20present%2C%20who%20had%20called%20the%20genocide%20the%20biggest%20failure%20of%20his%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rwandan%20Patriotic%20Front%20(RPF)%20rebel%20group%20captured%20Kigali%20in%20July%201994%20after%20a%20100-day%20killing%20spree%20that%20started%20on%20April%207%2C%201994%2C%20and%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20almost%20800%2C000%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20Tutsis%20but%20also%20moderate%20Hutus%2C%20according%20to%20Al%20Jazeera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Dammu%20Ravi%2C%20the%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(Economic%20Relations)%2C%20is%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20Rwanda%2C%20Uganda%2C%20and%20Kenya%20from%20April%207-12%2C%20accompanied%20by%20the%20Additional%20Secretary%20(East%20and%20Southern%20Africa)%2C%20Puneet%20R%20Kundal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20(April%207)%2C%20Dammu%20Ravi%20called%20on%20MoS%20for%20Foreign%20Affairs%20James%20Kabarebe%2C%20Minister%20of%20Finance%20and%20Economic%20Planning%20Uzziel%20Ndagijimana%20and%20MoS%20for%20Agriculture%20Eric%20Rwigamba%20of%20Rwanda%20in%20Kigali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecy%20(ER)%20Dammu%20Ravi%20called%20on%20MoS%20for%20Foreign%20Affairs%20James%20Kabarebe%2C%20Minister%20of%20Finance%20and%20Economic%20Planning%20Uzziel%20Ndagijimana%20and%20MoS%20for%20Agriculture%20Eric%20Rwigamba%20of%20Rwanda%20in%20Kigali.%20Discussions%20covered%20issues%20of%20bilateral%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MEA%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20hold%20meetings%20with%20Ministers%20and%20senior%20officials%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Rwanda%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MEA%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20will%20also%20meet%20with%20ministers%20and%20officials%20of%20the%20Ugandan%20government%2C%20besides%20chairing%20a%20business%20session%20comprising%20captains%20of%20Indian%20and%20Ugandan%20industry.%20He%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20Uganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20press%20release%20disclosed%20that%20%26quot%3BSecretary%20(ER)%20will%20then%20travel%20to%20Kenya%20heading%20a%20large%20delegation%20comprising%20officials%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%2C%20Indian%20agricultural%20companies%20and%20business%20chambers%20from%20April%2010-12.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20visit%20will%20fulfill%20the%20decision%20taken%20in%20the%20meeting%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20the%20President%20of%20Kenya%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20India%20in%20December%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delegation%20will%2C%20inter%20alia%2C%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20agricultural%20farming%20in%20Kenya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712541900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F2tg0f4u8_qutub-minar-rwanda-genocide-_625x300_08_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-qutub-minar-illuminates-in-remembrance-of-rwanda-genocide-of-1994-5395830%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Qutub%20Minar%20was%20lit%20up%20with%20the%20colours%20of%20the%20Rwandan%20national%20flag%20on%20Sunday%20in%20soli