h%20a%20series%20of%20attacks%20against%20the%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20Moraes%20threatening%20to%20%26quot%3Bcut%20off%20access%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20platform%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20will%20probably%20lose%20all%20revenue%20in%20Brazil%20and%20have%20to%20shut%20down%20our%20office%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20principles%20matter%20more%20than%20profit.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20divisive%20judicial%20figure%20--%20tyrannical%20to%20some%20and%20a%20fervent%20defender%20of%20democracy%20to%20others%20--%20Moraes%20is%20one%20of%20the%2011%20members%20on%20Brazil's%20high%20court.%20He%20also%20presides%20over%20the%20country's%20Superior%20Electoral%20Tribunal%2C%20or%20TSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%2C%20now%20including%20Musk%2C%20have%20said%20Moraes%20is%20part%20of%20a%20sweeping%20crackdown%20against%20free%20speech%20in%20Brazil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoraes%20has%20spearheaded%20the%20battle%20against%20disinformation%20in%20Brazil.%20In%20recent%20years%20he%20has%20ordered%20the%20blocking%20of%20accounts%20of%20influential%20figures%20on%20social%20networks%2C%20most%20of%20them%20supporters%20of%20Jair%20Bolsonaro.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%20the%20far-right%20former%20president%20was%20declared%20ineligible%20to%20run%20for%20office%20by%20the%20Moraes-led%20TSE%2C%20for%20disseminating%20false%20information%20about%20Brazil's%20electoral%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBolsonaro%20is%20also%20being%20investigated%20over%20an%20attempted%20coup%20to%20prevent%20his%202022%20electoral%20defeat%20against%20the%20current%20leftist%20president%2C%20Luiz%20Inacio%20Lula%20da%20Silva%2C%20after%20a%20crowd%20of%20Bolsonaro%20supporters%20stormed%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20country's%20three%20branches%20of%20power%20in%20Brasilia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20publish