20suffered%20a%20side%20strain%20and%20left%20the%20field%20after%20bowling%20just%20one%20over%20for%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20in%20their%20IPL%20match%20against%20Gujarat%20Titans.%20The%2021-year-old%20came%20to%20bowl%20in%20the%20fourth%20over%20of%20Titans'%20chase%20of%20164%2C%20but%20he%20could%20clock%20in%20excess%20of%20140%20kmph%20only%20twice%20in%20the%20over%20before%20walking%20off%20the%20field%20with%20the%20LSG%20physio.%20He%20conceded%2013%20runs%20in%20that%20over%20and%20did%20not%20return%20to%20the%20field%20thereafter%2C%20even%20as%20LSG%20registered%20a%2033-run%20win%20over%20GT.%20Later%2C%20Lucknow%20all-rounder%20Krunal%20Pandya%20said%20the%20young%20pacer%20seemed%20alright%20after%20coming%20off%20the%20field.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20brief%20chat%20(with%20Mayank)%20and%20he%20seemed%20okay%2C%20which%20is%20a%20positive.%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20conversation%20I%20have%20had%2C%20whatever%20we%20see%2C%20he%20has%20a%20good%20head%20on%20his%20shoulder.%20Really%20excited%20to%20see%20how%20his%20career%20pans%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Krunal%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20the%20reoccurrence%20of%20an%20injury%20that%20kept%20him%20on%20the%20benches%20during%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20season%20for%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayank%2C%20who%20had%20earlier%20struggled%20with%20ankle%20and%20hamstring%20niggles%20in%20his%20career%2C%20made%20his%20IPL%20debut%20this%20season%20against%20Punjab%20Kings%20and%20made%20an%20instant%20impression%20with%20his%20ability%20to%20breach%20the%20150%20kmph%20mark%20effortlessly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20second%20IPL%20match%20against%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20right-arm%20fast%20bowler%20took%20three%20for%2014%20and%20also%20bowled%20a%20156.7%20kmph%20delivery%2C%20the%20fastest%20of%20this%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayank%20bettered%20his%20own%20mark%20of%20155.8%20delivery%20that%20he%20bowled%20against%20the%20Punjab%20outfit%20in%20the%20previous%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20so%20far%20taken%20six%20wickets%20from%20two%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20West%20Indian%20pacer%20Ian%20Bishop%20underlined%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20Mayank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20should%20be%20treated%20and%20protected%20well%20as%20it%20is%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20his%20career.%20His%20body%20should%20get%20stronger%20considering%20he%20bowls%20at%20such%20a%20high%20pace%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20franchise%20and%20the%20country's%20board%20should%20take%20note%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Bishop%20said%20in%20the%20commentary%2C%20while%20giving%20the%20example%20of%20how%20Australia%20preserved%20Pat%20Cummins%20in%20his%20early%20years%20after%20the%20premier%20pacer%20suffered%20stress%20injury%20on%20his%20lower%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELucknow%20Super%20Giants%20was%20clinical%20while%20registering%20a%2033-run%20win%20over%20Gujarat%20Titans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20side%20could%20not%20mount%20a%20strong%20chase%20of%20164%2C%20and%20ended%20at%20130%20all%20out%20as%20LSG''s%20pacer%20Yash%20Thakur%20(5%2F30)%20and%20spinner%20Krunal%20Pandya%20(3%2F11)%20came%20up%20with%20impact%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20GT%2C%20only%20opener%20B%20Sai%20Sudharsan%20(31%2C%2023b)%20could%20offer%20some%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Marcus%20Stoinis%20made%20a%20fine%20fifty%20as%20LSG%20made%20163%20for%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELSG%20rode%20on%20Stoinis'%20(58%2C%2043b%2C%204x4s%2C%202x6s)%20solid%20effort%20to%20reach%20a%20par%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20contributions%20came%20from%20skipper%20KL%20Rahul%20(33%2C%2031b)%20and%20Nicholas%20Pooran%20(32%2C%2022b).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20GT%2C%20pacers%20Umesh%20Yadav%20and%20Darshan%20Nalkande%20took%20two%20wickets%20apiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712513880000%2C%22visual%