n-gaza-ahead-of-this-years-contest-13110494%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20marquee%20GOP%20Senate%20recruit%20and%20ex-Navy%20SEAL%20admits%20he%20lied%20about%20how%20he%20received%20a%20gunshot%20wound%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tim%20Sheehy%2C%20a%20former%20Navy%20SEAL%20and%20businessman%20recruited%20by%20GOP%20leaders%20to%20run%20against%20Democratic%20Sen.%20Jon%20Tester%20in%20Montana.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d3f8a1ec14ba0019f3a2d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETim%20Sheehy%2C%20a%20former%20Navy%20SEAL%20and%20businessman%20recruited%20by%20GOP%20leaders%20to%20run%20against%20Democratic%20Sen.%20Jon%20Tester%20in%20Montana.%3Cp%3ETim%20Sheehy%20for%20Montana%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMontana%20GOP%20Senate%20candidate%20Tim%20Sheehy%20told%20WaPo%20he%20lied%20about%20how%20he%20got%20a%20gunshot%20wound.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESheehy%20told%20a%20park%20ranger%20in%202015%20that%20he%20was%20shot%20after%20his%20firearm%20accidentally%20discharged.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20Sheehy%20recently%20admitted%20he%20was%20shot%20in%20uncertain%20circumstances%20while%20serving%20in%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMontana%20Senate%20candidate%20Tim%20Sheehy%2C%20a%20former%20Navy%20SEAL%20and%20one%20of%20GOP's%20star%20recruits%20of%20the%202024%20election%20cycle%2C%20admitted%20to%20The%20Washington%20Post%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2F2024%2F04%2F06%2Ftim-sheehy-montana-senate-gunshot-wound-national-park%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20lied%20to%20a%20National%20Park%20Service%20ranger%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20being%20shot%20during%20a%202015%20incident%20at%20the%20state's%20Glacier%20National%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20admission%20comes%20after%20Sheehy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-sheehy-montana-wealthy-republican-climate-change-china-investments-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20wealthy%20aerospace%20executive%3C%2Fa%3E%20who's%20aiming%20to%20take%20on%20three-term%20Democratic%20Sen.%20Jon%20Tester%2C%20had%20previously%20given%20inconsistent%20statements%20about%20how%20he%20was%20shot%20in%20his%20right%20arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202015%2C%20Sheehy%20informed%20a%20ranger%20that%20he%20had%20shot%20himself%20in%20the%20right%20arm%20after%20his%20Colt%20.45%20revolver%20fell%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20discharged%2C%20according%20to%20records%20filed%20in%20the%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20District%20of%20Montana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Post%2C%20a%20description%20of%20the%20incident%20contained%20within%20a%20federal%20citation%20noted%20that%20the%20gunshot%20left%20a%20bullet%20in%20Sheehy's%20right%20arm.%20The%20written%20details%20of%20the%20citation%2C%20which%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20ranger%2C%20were%20based%20on%20Sheehy's%20recounting%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheehy%20ended%20up%20paying%20a%20%24525%20fine%20over%20his%20gun%20discharging%20in%20a%20national%20park%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20at%20the%20time%20was%20based%20on%20his%20report%20to%20the%20ranger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20by%20the%20Post%20about%20the%20ranger's%20citation%2C%20Sheehy%20said%20he%20fabricated%20the%20story%20about%20the%20gun%20discharging%20to%20shield%20himself%20and%20his%20former%20platoon%20members%20from%20being%20probed%20over%20a%20gunshot%20wound%20that%20he%20said%20he%20received%20while%20in%20Afghanistan%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheehy%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20he%20fell%20and%20injured%20himself%20during%20a%202015%20hike%20at%20Glacier%20National%20Park%2C%20which%20prompted%20a%20hospital%20visit.%20While%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20he%20informed%20the%20staff%20that%20there%20was%20a%20bullet%20lodged%20in%20his%20arm%2C%20which%20led%20to%20him%20being%20questioned%20by%20the%20ranger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20guess%20the%20only%20thing%20I'm%20guilty%20of%20is%20admitting%20to%20doing%20something%20I%20never%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheehy%20told%20the%20Post%2C%20affirming%20that%20his%20gun%20never%20went%20off%20at%20the%20national%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Sheehy%20defended%20what%20he%20said%20was%20his%20attempt%20to%20keep%20his%20former%20platoon%20members%20out%20of%20any%20investigations.%20He%20told%20the%20Post%20he%20was%20unsure%20if%20his%20bullet%20wound%20was%20the%20result%20of%20friendly%20fire%20or%20from%20an%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20a%20whole%20team%20of%20really%20great%20Americans%20didn't%20get%20dragged%20through%20the%20mud%20over%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20a%20crime%20to%20lie%20to%20a%20federal%20officer%2C%20the%20Post%20reported%20that%20the%20statute%20of%20limitations%20regarding%20the%20incident%20has%20expired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Watkins%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20Sheehy%2C%20said%20Sheehy%20had%20not%20impeded%20a%20law%20enforcement%20probe%20because%20no%20crime%20had%20taken%20place%20at%20the%20national%20park%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheehy's%20admission%20came%20as%20inconsistencies%20piled%20up%20regarding%20how%20he%20was%20shot%20while%20serving%20in%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sheehy%20campaign%20provided%20an%20x-ray%20to%20the%20Post%20with%20the%20condition%20that%20it%20could%20be%20sent%20to%20experts%20but%20not%20published%20by%20the%20newspaper.%20A%20professor%20and%20longtime%20trauma%20surgeon%20who%20reviewed%20the%20x-ray%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20he%20found%20it%20%26quot%3Bdoubtful%26quot%3B%20that%20Sheehy's%20wound%20came%20from%20an%20assault%20weapon%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20it%20likely%20came%20from%20a%20handgun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Sheehy's%202023%20memoir%2C%20%26quot%3BMudslingers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20that%20he%20had%20been%20shot%20once%20while%20serving%20in%20Afghanistan.%20But%20in%20another%20passage%2C%20he%20wrote%20that%20he%20had%20been%20shot%20multiple%20times%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheehy%20was%20awarded%20the%20Bronze%20Star%20and%20the%20Purple%20Heart%20for%20separate%20events%20for%20serving%20in%20combat%20overseas%2C%20and%20neither%20award%20is%20in%20dispute%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailybeast.com%2Fgop-montana-candidate-tim-sheehy-says-he-lied-to-ranger-in-2015-about-how-he-was-shot%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20The%20Daily%20Beast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sheehy's%20campaign%20said%20that%20the%20GOP%20candidate%20%26quot%3Bwon't%20ever%20let%20any%20of%20this%20slander%20stop%20him%20from%20fighting%20every%20day%20as%20your%20next%20US%20Senator.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20Montanans%20respect%20his%20selfless%20sacrifice%20for%20our%20country%20and%20commend%20it%2C%20because%20he%20is%20a%20Republican%20running%20for%20office%2C%20the%20liberal%20elite%20misinformation%20machine%20is%20going%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20question%20and%20attack%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Sheehy%20campaign%20for%20further%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheehy%20is%20heavily%20favored%20to%20win%20the%20June%204%20GOP%20Senate%20primary%20and%20has%20been%20highly%20touted%20by%20Washington%20Republicans%20as%20one%20of%20their%20strongest%20candidates%20to%20date%20against%20Tester%2C%20who%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-senate-races-2024-election-landscape-democrats-republicans-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20withstood%20the%20political%20headwinds%20for%20Democrats%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20conse