isit%20to%20Bandarban%20where%20he%20said%20a%20military-led%20clampdown%20against%20the%20KNF%20has%20started%20to%20eliminate%20the%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20some%20KNF%20members%20were%20arrested%20and%20weapons%20were%20recovered%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20being%20cornered%20last%20June%2C%20they%20(KNF)%20appeared%20willing%20to%20negotiate.%20Unfortunately%2C%20their%20commitment%20to%20peace%20was%20superficial%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20their%20continued%20involvement%20in%20criminal%20acts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20army%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBandarban's%20autonomous%20hill%20district%20council%20chief%20Kya%20Shai%20Hla%20last%20year%20took%20the%20initiative%20to%20convince%20KNF%20members%20to%20return%20to%20normal%20life%20under%20a%20peace%20negotiation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20process%20was%20derailed%20as%20the%20outfit%20last%20week%20carried%20out%20two%20attacks%20on%20three%20branches%20of%20state-run%20banks%2C%20looted%20weapons%20from%20security%20guards%20of%20the%20banks%2C%20and%20kidnapped%20a%20bank%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20manager%20was%20released%20after%20three%20days%20through%20mediation%2C%20but%20the%20KNF's%20latest%20act%20prompted%20the%20tribal%20district%20council%20chief%20to%20suspend%20the%20peace%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKNF%20members%20last%20year%20killed%20three%20soldiers%20and%20wounded%20a%20few%20others%20in%20Bandarban%20during%20a%20security%20clampdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20officials%20have%20said%20the%20KNF%20emerged%20as%20an%20armed%20group%20mostly%20comprising%20people%20from%20the%20Christian-majority%20Bom%20tribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20the%20outfit%20earlier%20allied%20with%20a%20newly%20formed%20Islamist%20militant%20group%20called%20Jama'atul%20Ansar%20Fil%20Hindal%20Sharqiya%2C%20which%20took%20refuge%20in%20the%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20KNF%20offered%20armed%20training%20to%20the%20Islamist%20group%20members%20in%20exchange%20for%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20had%20seen%20the%20end%20of%20a%20nearly%20two-decade-long%20hill%20insurgency%20in%201997%20with%20the%20signing%20of%20a%20peace%20agreement%20between%20the%20government%20and%20Parbatya%20Chattagram%20Jana%20Sanghati%20Samity%20(PCJSS)%20or%20JSS%2C%20which%20had%20been%20demanding%20regional%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bom%20tribe%20had%20little%20involvement%20during%20the%20JSS%20armed%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712513160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fkgimbsvo_cheosim-bom_625x300_07_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-hid-inside-locker-says-bangladesh-military-as-they-arrest-kuki-chin-national-front-leader-cheosim-bom-5394762%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bangladesh's%20security%20agencies%20on%20Sunday%20arrested%20a%20senior%20commander%20of%20a%20tribal%20insurgent%20group%20believed%20to%20have%20links%20with%20an%20Islamist%20terrorist%20organisation%2C%20days%20after%20the%20outfit%20looted%20state-owned%20banks%20and%20abducted%20a%20bank%20manager.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-hid-inside-locker-says-bangladesh-military-as-they-arrest-kuki-chin-national-front-leader-cheosim-bom-5394762%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-hid-inside-locker-says-bangladesh-military-as-they-arrest-kuki-chin-national-front-leader-cheosim-bom-5394762%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-hid-inside-locker-says-bangladesh-military-as-they-arrest-kuki-chin-national-front-leader-cheosim-bom-5394762%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20to%20invest%20Rs%202.3%20trillion%20in%20renewable%20energy%2C%20manufacturing%20capacity%22%2C%22content