s%20an%20armilla%20bracelet%20was%20given%20to%20the%20Roman%20soldiers%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20respect%20and%20valour%20and%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20brilliantly%20fascinating.%20We%20have%20learned%20so%20many%20things%20and%20it%20is%20quite%20lovely%20to%20still%20be%20involved%2C%20so%20we%20can%20follow%20its%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%2C%20'Wow%2C%20imagine%20who%20wore%20that'.%20We've%20had%20a%20piece%20of%20history%20in%20our%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712512260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ftojm3jso_rowan-brannan-_625x300_07_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-boy-finds-rare-2-000-year-old-gold-bracelet-while-walking-his-dog-5395007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20metal%20was%20caked%20with%20dirt%2C%20but%20the%20boy%20kept%20holding%20it%20and%20was%20convinced%20that%20it%20could%20be%20actual%20gold.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-boy-finds-rare-2-000-year-old-gold-bracelet-while-walking-his-dog-5395007%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-boy-finds-rare-2-000-year-old-gold-bracelet-while-walking-his-dog-5395007%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-boy-finds-rare-2-000-year-old-gold-bracelet-while-walking-his-dog-5395007%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20is%20now%20analyzing%20your%20garbage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lettuce%20in%20a%20garbage%20bin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6612cb9f1caec1275a6d8f94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECompanies%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20tackle%20food%20waste.%3Cp%3E%C2%A9Studio%20One-One%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3