first%20client.%20We%20have%20a%20production%20agreement%20with%20the%20BBC%2C%20and%20we%20will%20be%20producing%20content%20for%20the%20BBC%20across%20its%20six%20different%20language%20services%20and%20India's%20English%20YouTube%20channel%2C%26quot%3B%20Rupa%20Jha%2C%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20the%20Collective%20Newsroom%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20keep%20the%20BBC%20Editorial%20Guidelines%20in%20mind%20when%20producing%20content%20for%20them%2C%20such%20as%20the%20kind%20of%20journalism%20the%20BBC%20practices.%20Upholding%20the%20trust%20in%20the%20BBC%20brand%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20carry%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20will%20do%20will%20be%20completely%20aligned%20with%20the%20journalistic%20values%20of%20the%20BBC.%20We%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20BBC%2C%20and%20the%20BBC%20has%20faith%20in%20us%3B%20that%20is%20why%20we%20are%20undertaking%20all%20of%20this.%20We%20have%20to%20conduct%20journalism%20that%20can%20be%20trusted%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restructuring%20was%20prompted%20by%20the%20new%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investment%20(FDI)%20rules%2C%20which%20were%20introduced%20in%202020%2C%20that%20imposed%20a%2026%25%20FDI%20limit%20in%20India's%20digital%20media%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompanies%20exceeding%20the%2026%25%20FDI%20limit%20were%20required%20to%20reduce%20their%20foreign%20investment%20to%20comply%20with%20this%20regulation%20by%20October%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E99.99%25%20of%20BBC%20World%20Service%20India's%20shares%20are%20owned%20by%20its%20UK-based%20public%20broadcaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20has%20sought%20a%2026%25%20stake%20in%20its%20recently%20established%20Collective%20Newsroom%20company%2C%20a%20source%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20a%20number%20of%20options%20before%20us.%20Considering%20that%20the%20BBC%20didn't%20want%20to%20lose%20its%20presence%20in%20India%20or%20cut%20jobs%2C%20and%20they%20didn't%20want%20it%20to%20become%20financially%20unviable%2C%20this%20forced%20us%20to%20think%20out%20of%20the%20box.%20Based%20on%20the%20legal%20advice%20the%20BBC%20was%20receiving%2C%20everyone%20was%20veering%20towards%20this%20as%20the%20viable%20option%20(of%20setting%20up%20the%20Collective)%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Jha%20was%20quoted%20saying%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fafter-tax-searches-fdi-questions-bbc-hives-off-newsroom-in-india-as-separate-company-9255471%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETax%20searches%20were%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20BBC's%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%20offices%C2%A0in%20February%20last%20year%20after%20it%20aired%20a%20controversial%20two-part%20series%20titled%20'India%3A%20The%20Modi%20Question'%20that%20featured%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712511840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ff5bqib6o_bbc-_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbbc-india-restructures-business-after-centre-tweaks-fdi-rules-5394731%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BBC%20has%20handed%20over%20its%20newsroom%20publishing%20licence%20in%20India%20to%20a%20private%20limited%20company%2C%20Collective%20Newsroom%20-%20a%20first%20for%20the%20public%20service%20broadcaster's%20global%20operations%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbbc-india-restructures-business-after-centre-tweaks-fdi-rules-5394731%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbbc-india-restructures-business-after-centre-tweaks-fdi-rules-5394731%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbbc-india-restructures-business-after-centre-tweaks-fdi-rules-5394731%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22