noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333208%2Fwhere-to-eat-in-kolkata-classics-best-heritage-eateries-map-anindya-basu-dolon-dutta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20seasoned%20sweet%20shop%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20to%20amass%20a%20great%20crowd%2C%20and%20among%20them%20was%20Sir%20Ashutosh%20Mukherjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3ELifestyle%20Asia%3C%2Fem%3E%20tells%20an%20anecdote%20of%20how%20Lady%20Canning%2C%20wife%20of%20the%20then%20viceroy%20of%20India%2C%20Charles%20John%20Canning%2C%20was%20once%20visiting%20erstwhile%20Calcutta%20in%201858%20and%20wanted%20a%20special%20sweet%20made%20for%20her%20birthday.%20Nag%20took%20up%20the%20challenge!%20And%20it%20is%20this%20creation%20that%20was%20named%20after%20Lady%20Canning%2C%20which%20over%20the%20years%20became%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eledikeni%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Flury%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20hub%20that%20saw%20a%20flurry%20of%20activity%2C%20this%20outlet%20on%20Park%20Street%20was%20founded%20in%20the%20year%201927%20by%20a%20couple%20Mr%20and%20Mrs%20J%20Flury.%20It%20was%20frequented%20by%20some%20of%20the%20most%20notable%20names%20in%20both%20Indian%20and%20British%20history.%20A%20favourite%20tea%20room%20amongst%20the%20royal%20and%20politically%20inclined%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179380%2Ficonic-restaurants-kolkata-cabins-must-try-food-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20eatery%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20witnessed%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20single%20eatery%20on%20Park%20Street%20to%20over%2068%20outlets%20across%20India%2C%20Flury%E2%80%99s%20brand%20name%20has%20continued%20to%20garner%20love%20from%20across%20the%20world.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20eatery%20was%20featured%20on%20the%202023%20list%20of%20%E2%80%98150%20most%20