0down%20for%20at%20least%2050%20years%2C%20are%20resistant%20to%20floods.%20This%20is%20a%20vital%20trait%20in%20combating%20food%20security%20threats%20posed%20by%20climate%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20Neelam%2C%20now%2037%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20sadly%2C%20due%20to%20the%20increasing%20adoption%20of%20genetically%20modified%20hybrid%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20in%20the%20Northeast%20are%20abandoning%20heirloom%20varieties.%20This%2C%20coupled%20with%20frequent%20floods%2C%20has%20made%20agriculture%20unsustainable%20in%20the%20region.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neelam%20says%20he%20wanted%20the%20local%20farmers%20in%20his%20region%20to%20wholeheartedly%20adopt%20and%20switch%20to%20heirloom%20seeds.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-1712121263-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346319%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeelam%20says%20he%20wanted%20the%20local%20farmers%20in%20his%20region%20to%20wholeheartedly%20adopt%20and%20switch%20to%20heirloom%20seeds.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20solution%20lies%20in%20preserving%20these%20heirloom%20seeds%2C%20which%20serve%20as%20an%20essential%20resource%20for%20farmers%20striving%20to%20adjust%20to%20climate%20change.%20I%20wanted%20to%20show%20them%20why%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20conserve%20our%20agricultural%20heritage%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neelam%2C%20who%20went%20on%20to%20promote%20the%20cultivation%20of%20heirloom%20seeds%20in%20his%20region.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20conserved%20over%201%2C000%20heirloom%20seed%20varieties%20of%20vegetables%20and%20rice%2C%20and%20trained%20at%20least%2024%2C000%20other%20farmers%20in%20seed%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claims%20his%20company%20%E2%80%98Pabhoi%20Greens%E2%80%99%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20first%20seed%20conservation%20company%20in%20the%20Northeast%E2%80%9D%20where%20farmers%20are%20propagating%20the%20organic%20seeds%20on%20their%20own.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%2C%20these%20farmers%20grow%20heirloom%20seeds%2C%20they%20preserve%20that%20diversity%20and%20ensure%20these%20seeds%20are%20available%20for%20future%20generations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EQuest%20of%20a%20farm%20boy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20childhood%2C%20Neelam%20recalls%20being%20compelled%20to%20study%20due%20to%20societal%20pressure.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20a%20farm%20boy!%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20agriculture%20like%20my%20father.%20He%20was%20a%20medical%20doctor%20by%20profession%20but%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20farm%20in%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%20But%20sadly%2C%20Neelam%E2%80%99s%20father%20passed%20away%20from%20a%20stroke%20while%20Neelam%20was%20studying%20in%20Class%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20completing%20Class%2012%2C%20I%20applied%20for%20graduation%20in%20arts%20from%20an%20open%20school.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20so%20disinterested%20that%20I%20neglected%20to%20submit%20assignments%20required%20to%20complete%20the%20degree%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20Pabho