n%20a%20matter%20of%208%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20keep%20the%20trays%20in%20my%20cupboard%20as%20we%20have%20to%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20sunlight.%20Since%20it%20grows%20in%208%20days%2C%20I%20get%20a%20sufficient%20yield%20in%20a%20month.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20pushing%20other%20farmers%20too%20to%20try%20hydroponics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20costs%20about%20Rs%2020%2C000.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%20explains%20the%20steps%20to%20grow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327478%2Fashwin-sawant-low-cost-hydroponics-model-helps-farmers-grow-fodder-save-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaize%20fodder%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20a%20hydroponics%20unit%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWash%20and%20soak%20the%20grains%20for%2024%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETie%20the%20seeds%20in%20a%20gunny%20bag%20and%20keep%20it%20in%20water%20for%2024%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETransfer%20the%20sprouted%20seeds%20to%20a%20tray%20and%20spread%20it%20out.%20Keep%20it%20in%20the%20cupboard.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWater%20it%20once%20every%20three%20hours%2C%20either%20manually%20or%20using%20a%20sprinkler%20with%20a%20timer%20for%207%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20yield%20will%20be%20ready%20on%20the%208th%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Cem%3EPicture%20credits%3A%20P%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712147266000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan-min-1712145955.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22P%20Saravanan%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20uses%20hydroponics%20to%20grow%20maize%20fodder%20for%20his%20cattle.%20He%20has%20also%20found%20a%20way%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20pesticides%20and%20keep%20his%20pr